    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home your absolute dream car? I'm parting with this total gem and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one\u2014the paint is sparkling and the interior is just pristine. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You\u2019ve really gotta see this one in person to believe how perfect it is. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of analog engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically pristine; the critical rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the Double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal camshaft timing and torque delivery. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and factory-calibrated dampers that preserve the vehicle\u2019s legendary turn-in response. The exterior finish is flawless, and the interior retains its structural integrity with no bolster wear or electronic pixel failure. A collector-grade specimen optimized for the purist driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. Flawless interior and exterior. Zero mechanical issues. Clean title in hand. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features flawless original paint with a professional ceramic coating, showing zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are protected by factory mats, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a thick folder of records to prove it. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather driving. This is a smoke-free, pet-free, single-owner vehicle that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
